cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper involves the use of computer vision and machine learning algorithms to classify algae cells based on their spectral and morphological features. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of machine learning algorithms also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of data, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
